controller.util.solutionattribute

Class Generation<S extends Solution<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.metaheuristic.util.solutionattribute.SolutionAttribute<S,java.lang.Integer>
      • controller.util.solutionattribute.Generation<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the type of solution.

    public class Generation<S extends Solution<?>>
extends SolutionAttribute<S,java.lang.Integer>
    This attribute is used to save the number of generation realized by the algorithm when it finish his execution. Notes:

    This attribute is used by the GUI. If it is used by an algorithm this will be overwritten when the GUI execute the algorithm.
    This attribute is used by SingleObjectiveExperimentTask and MultiObjectiveExperimentTask to save the generation when the result was generated.
